{"tid":1388270,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無所謂中計唔中計, 行我地要行嘅路","createTime":"2019-07-30T16:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T16:18:40.000Z","uid":281532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7fb4b46531a5029655171d2551dbbd82ade59ac0","tid":1388270,"uid":281532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:18:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/07/29/chenglap-the-ravages-of-time/#.XUBqQwsGifV.link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2019%2F07%2F29%2Fchenglap-the-ravages-of-time%2F%23.XUBqQwsGifV.link&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=c8bcc850\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/07/29/chenglap-the-ravages-of-time/#.XUBqQwsGifV.link</a><br />\n<br />\n傘運以黎香港人一直行出<br />\n一個又一個奇蹟<br />\n我地係奇兵<br />\n奇兵強在<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無部署</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> Improvisation</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即場做決定</span><br />\n連登吹咩風唔重要<br />\n因為大家目標一致<br />\n我相信我地可以再創造奇蹟<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n撤回，引渡條例<br />\n撤銷，暴動定義<br />\n撤控，傷者學生<br />\n徹查，黑警暴力<br />\n撤職，查辦林鄭<br />\n<br />\n而保證五大訴求唔係做假，就只有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">雙普選</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油!!!"}]}